item.description:
Hi all,
This is one of the nail biting challenges of our industry, failing in running a straight-forward task. Especially when it is failing&hellip;
What happened? I was creating a pipeline in Azure DevOps to deploy an ARM template for VM setups with VM Extensions. To prep this deployment, the artifacts (DSC scripts) should be copied to Azure Blob Storage, in order for the Azure DevOps build agent to &ldquo;find&rdquo; it.
